about.summary: Basic infrastructure and some algorithms for the traveling salesperson problem (also traveling salesman problem; TSP). The package provides some simple algorithms and an interface to the Concorde TSP solver and its implementation of the Chained-Lin-Kernighan heuristic. The code for Concorde itself is not included in the package and has to be obtained separately.

name: r-tsp
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.1-10" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tsp
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/TSP_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/TSP/TSP_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 44979f16803806419a94a6b0daeac812f4e7bd52d2fff11561fd4bbc41353b7c

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-foreach
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-foreach

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('TSP')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('TSP')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/mhahsler/TSP
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Basic infrastructure and some algorithms for the traveling salesperson problem (also traveling salesman problem; TSP). The package provides some simple
    algorithms and an interface to the Concorde TSP solver and its implementation of the Chained-Lin-Kernighan heuristic. The code for Concorde itself is not included
    in the package and has to be obtained separately.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - MathiasHaudgaard
    - FrodePedersen
    - ArneKr
    - conda-forge/r
